#compdef repairHomePermissions
# Documentation: https://eclecticlight.co/2020/02/18/repairing-permissions-in-your-home-folder-has-changed/
# Reference accessed: 2026-05-17
# Verified: upstream docs at the URL above.

local curcontext="$curcontext" state line ret=1

